00:27:28.520 --> 00:27:29.980
you end up with this.

00:27:29.980 --> 00:27:31.760
And once you know
this formula, it's

00:27:31.760 --> 00:27:36.720
far, far easier
than to calculate

00:27:36.720 --> 00:27:38.889
all this in terms of
thetas and theta dots,

00:27:38.889 --> 00:27:39.805
and sines and cosines.

00:27:44.730 --> 00:27:45.230
OK?

00:27:47.961 --> 00:27:48.460
All right.

00:27:48.460 --> 00:27:49.000
That's good.

